      <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;background:#F0FFFE;border:1px solid #B2F5EA;border-radius:14px;padding:24px;">
        <p style="font-weight:700;color:#1A202C;margin:0 0 14px;font-size:1rem;">What Affects the Cost?</p>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:#4B5563;font-size:0.95rem;line-height:1.9;">
          {costFactors.map(c => <li>{c}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="color:#6B7280;font-size:0.98rem;line-height:1.8;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">Most cases finish within a few days or a few weeks, though some documents require additional verification that can increase the timeline. Documents issued outside the UAE go through more verification stages, so the total cost becomes higher compared to local documents. Many people who require Divorce Certificate Attestation Services in Dubai and Abu Dhabi contact experts first to understand the exact process and expected cost before starting the procedure.</p>
  </div>
